      "date": "2015-05-15 15:06:54.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: -Code-Review\n\nthe problem here is for the import state of MGC is \"FULL\" when doing mount, otherwise it will the import state\nin mgc_process_log, the patch here is wait a little to allow the client to find the connection to MGS is broken by ping\nand reconnect to it. then \"wait_clients_import_state\" could not fix the problem here for the CONNECTING, RECOVER\nstates are intermediate and it can be changed between the wait interval (1s).",
